products.title: Out 'N Back - Medium Dark Blend
products.description:
Out 'N Back is an electrolyte infused coffee, best for athletes who don't do well with geographical directions. Drink coffee, run one direction, run back the same direction, drink another coffee. 

This is a blend of medium roast & dark roast, delivering smooth flavor that isn't too fruity or too bold.

products.title: Reusable LRC Pod
products.description:
Most single-use coffee pods are not recyclable. That's bad. And an estimated 62 billion single-use pods are consumed annually. That's also bad. 

But all is not lost! With these reusable cartridges, you can Fuel Your Passion with Long Run Coffee without maiming the planet. 

Compatible with most single serve brewers.
